eut prendre pour miroir réflexif, l’inventeur du mot énergie, Aristote.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 0aMechanicsxSources. 0aMechanics. 0aPhysicsxHistory. 0aSciencexHistory. 4aGeneral Physics. 4aHistory of science. 7aSCIENCE / Philosophy & Social Aspects.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020z978311075640108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2018z978311102388540uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-2268-340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759822683423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759822683/original  a978-3-11-075640-1  EDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020c2016d2020  a978-3-11-102388-5  EDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2018b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK